<title>AUSTRALIA: BHP makes senior appointments.</title>
<headline>BHP makes senior appointments.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-07-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Broken Hill Pty Co Ltd (BHP) on Tuesday announced a number of senior appointments, affecting its Melbourne head office, effective August 1.</p>
<p>BHP said Garry Evans, group general manager human resources and external affairs at BHP Steel, would take on the new position of corporate general manager corporate services.</p>
<p>Lance Hockridge, currently corporate general manager international, would take over Evans' role at BHP Steel.</p>
<p>Bob Flew, having completed his secondment with BHP Copper as senior vice president corporate development, would return to the position of corporate general manager international.</p>
<p>-- Sydney Newsroom 61-2 9373-1800</p>
